## 📋 Aide-mémoire

**Checklist CI/CD** :

- [ ] Pipeline CI/CD automatisé
- [ ] Stages standardisés (lint, test, build, scan, deploy, health, notify)
- [ ] Tests bloquants
- [ ] Scan sécurité (Trivy, Snyk)
- [ ] Versioning images
- [ ] Rollback automatique
- [ ] Backup avant déploiement
- [ ] Validation configuration
- [ ] Notifications équipe
- [ ] Timeout pipeline
- [ ] Déploiements par environnement
- [ ] Registry privé

**Pattern pipeline Jenkins** :

```groovy
pipeline {
    agent any
    options {
        timeout(time: 20, unit: 'MINUTES')
    }
    stages {
        stage('Checkout') { }
        stage('Lint') { }
        stage('Test') { }
        stage('Build') { }
        stage('Scan') { }
        stage('Backup') { }
        stage('Deploy') { }
        stage('Health Check') { }
    }
    post {
        success { /* notify */ }
        failure { /* rollback + notify */ }
    }
}
```
